    "causal_summary": "This is **Phase 16** under `002-spec-memory-stack`. The packet closes a latent regression that surfaced after ADR-012 (canonical vector shard split) and ADR-013 (nomic default) shipped: the runtime KNN search path was reading an empty `vec_memories` table because reindex only wrote the canonical `vec_<dim>` table, and the factory was scanning the wrong file for the dim-tagged pointer table.",
